		<h2>Behind the scenes</h2>
		<p>Katlynn is an accessibility advocate and ally, working to create a world that is able to be accessed by all. In 2018, Katlynn launched <a href="http://buildforall.ca/">Build for All</a>, a website empowering startups to create accessible products and&nbsp;services.</p>
		<p>Build for All’s goal is to provide the community with education and processes on how to successfully implement accessible options, while addressing the fact that startups are already overburdened and are being pulled in many different directions. Everyone deserves access to technology, and everyone deserves access on equal terms.</p>
